ement, we\nalso tackle a previously-unsolved version of the constraint that addresses\noverlapping windows. Overall, the proposed framework generates state-of-the-art\nconstructions with significant ease while also enabling the simultaneous\nintegration of multiple constraints for the first time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 19:33:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
