 + \\sqrt n/\\epsilon^2\\right)$ for testing\nuniformity of distributions over $[n]$ under the parity trace, leading also to\nresults for the problems above.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 20:58:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
