 space comprised the HOMO and LUMO\norbitals needed for description of the diradical. We have also investigated the\nsensitivity of the results on orbital rotation of the HOMO-LUMO pair, as it is\nwell known that Hilbert-space MRCC methods are not invariant to such\ntransformations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 08:29:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
