t less than 5%\nof the detections from the multiscale method can be ascribed to line-of-sight\nalignments. The method is well-adapted to the more sensitive, wider-area,\noptical surveys that will be available in the near future, and paves the way to\ncluster samples that are as near as possible to being selected by total matter\ncontent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 14:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
