y and the energy density jump at the\nhadron-quark interface. We calculate the tidal deformabilities of SSHSs and\nanalyse them in the light of the GW170817 event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 15:48:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
